select `jumlah_barang`, `code`, `jenis_barang`, `berat`, `biaya` from `cargo_pengiriman_barangs` where `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` = 1 and `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` is not null and `no_lmt` = 1

select code,
berat,
jenis_barang,
kode_kotas.kota as asal,
status_pembayarans.pesan,
SUM(biaya) as biaya,
SUM(jumlah_barang) as jumlah_barang,
cargo_pengiriman_details.keterangan,
DATE(cargo_pengiriman_details.created_at) as created from `cargo_pengiriman_barangs` left join `cargo_pengiriman_details` on `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` = `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` left join `kode_kotas` on `kode_kotas`.`id_kode_kota` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_kode_kota_asal` left join `status_pembayarans` on `status_pembayarans`.`id_status_pembayaran` = `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`id_status_pembayaran` where `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` = 1 and `cargo_pengiriman_barangs`.`no_lmt` is not null and `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` = 1 group by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`no_lmt` order by `cargo_pengiriman_details`.`created_at` desc limit 1
